# Synapse Branding License

Copyright © 2026 Aromal J and the Synapse Project.
All Rights Reserved.

This package contains the official branding assets of the Synapse Project, including but not limited to:

* The Synapse name and project identity.
* Logos and logotypes.
* Icons.
* Wallpapers.
* Graphics and artwork.
* Other visual branding assets included in this package.

## Permitted Uses

The branding assets may be used for:

* Reviewing Synapse OS.
* Demonstrating or showcasing Synapse OS.
* Writing articles, documentation, or blog posts about Synapse OS.
* Creating educational material.
* Publishing screenshots, videos, livestreams, or other media featuring Synapse OS.
* Referring to the official Synapse Project.

Such use must not imply endorsement, sponsorship, or official affiliation unless explicitly authorized by the Synapse Project.

## Prohibited Uses

Without prior written permission from the Synapse Project, you may not:

* Use the Synapse name or branding to identify or promote another operating system, software project, product, organization, or service.
* Redistribute the branding assets as part of another project's identity.
* Modify the branding assets for use as branding for another project.
* Use the branding in any manner that may confuse users about the origin or authenticity of software.

## Scope

This license applies only to the branding assets contained in this package.

The software, source code, and other components of Synapse OS are licensed separately under their respective open-source licenses.
